{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idef24900c-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s2008g"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2008g"},"text":"§ 2008g.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Payment of interest as condition of loan servicing for borrowers","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary may not reschedule or reamortize a loan for a borrower under this chapter who has not requested consideration under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s1981d/e"},"text":"section 1981d(e) of this title","children":[],"tail":" unless the borrower pays a portion, as determined by the Secretary, of the interest due on the loan."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idef24900d-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/87/128/tIII/s372"},"text":"Pub. L. 87–128, title III, § 372","children":[],"tail":", as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/127/tVI/s648/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–127, title VI, § 648(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1996-04-04"},"text":"Apr. 4, 1996","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/110/1104"},"text":"110 Stat. 1104","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idef24900e-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idef24900f-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idef249010-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children"